description: A peaceful oasis in the big city! This apartment is centrally located and has gated parking. The room fills up with sunlight in the morning, has hardwood floors and custom furniture, plenty of books, a meditation cushion, art etc. You can get anywhere in the city quickly, east side or west. It is just off the 10 freeway. There are plenty of friendly people in the building--mostly other artists--who will leave you alone or help you depending on your mood. The underground museum is just down the block.
